---
/**
 * context-engineering 0006 · Figure 5 — the versioned golden set feeding offline
 * regression (CI) and online signals (production), looping back.
 *
 * Copied VERBATIM from the source lesson HTML (figure + svg + figcaption incl. the
 * footnote <sup>). Lives as an .astro component so the kebab-case SVG attributes
 * render byte-for-byte (see Fig1's header for the full rationale).
 *
 * The markers this figure references (arw, arwG) are inlined into its own <defs>,
 * since the MDX has no shared <body> <defs> block.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 640 250"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A versioned golden set feeds offline regression in CI; production feeds online signals; both report back to the golden set."
    >
        <defs>
            <marker
                id="arw"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#6b675f"></path></marker
            >
            <marker
                id="arwG"
                viewBox="0 0 10 10"
                refX="8.5"
                refY="5"
                markerWidth="7"
                markerHeight="7"
                orient="auto-start-reverse"
                ><path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z" fill="#2f5d3a"></path></marker
            >
        </defs>
        <text x="320" y="18" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11.5" font-weight="700" fill="#111110"
            >OFFLINE REGRESSION &amp; ONLINE SIGNALS</text
        >
        <!-- golden set -->
        <rect
            x="220"
            y="32"
            width="200"
            height="58"
            rx="10"
            fill="#f1eef2"
            stroke="#b5179e"
            stroke-width="2"></rect>
        <text x="320" y="54" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" font-weight="700" fill="#b5179e"
            >Golden set (versioned)</text
        >
        <text x="320" y="70" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
            >query · relevant doc IDs · ideal answer</text
        >
        <text x="320" y="83" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#6b675f"
            >synthetic generation + human curation</text
        >
        <!-- offline -->
        <rect
            x="40"
            y="128"
            width="240"
            height="84"
            rx="10"
            fill="#eef2f7"
            stroke="#1f3a5a"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="160" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" font-weight="700" fill="#1f3a5a"
            >Offline eval — in CI, pre-deploy</text
        >
        <text x="160" y="170" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
            >replay golden set &rarr; recall@k, nDCG,</text
        >
        <text x="160" y="184" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
            >faithfulness vs last release</text
        >
        <text x="160" y="202" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-style="italic" fill="#1f3a5a"
            >catches regressions before users do</text
        >
        <!-- online -->
        <rect
            x="360"
            y="128"
            width="240"
            height="84"
            rx="10"
            fill="#e9f3ec"
            stroke="#2f5d3a"
            stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
        <text x="480" y="150" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10.5" font-weight="700" fill="#2f5d3a"
            >Online eval — in production</text
        >
        <text x="480" y="170" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
            >thumbs up/down · deflection/escalation</text
        >
        <text x="480" y="184" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" fill="#6b675f"
            >citation-click · follow-up / rephrase rate</text
        >
        <text x="480" y="202" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9" font-style="italic" fill="#2f5d3a"
            >finds what offline missed</text
        >
        <!-- arrows -->
        <line x1="280" y1="70" x2="180" y2="126" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
        <line
            x1="480"
            y1="126"
            x2="400"
            y2="78"
            stroke="#2f5d3a"
            stroke-dasharray="4 3"
            marker-end="url(#arwG)"></line>
        <text x="540" y="104" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8" fill="#6b675f"
            >new failures feed back</text
        >
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        Two loops, one source of truth. <b>Offline</b> regression on the versioned golden set gates deploys;
        <b>online</b> signals surface real-world misses, which you curate <em>back into</em> the golden
        set so the next offline run catches them.<sup><a href="#s3" id="r3">3</a></sup>
    </figcaption>
</figure>
